<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">PersonIdentifier ()</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">CX</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Components: &lt;ID (ST)&gt; ^ &lt;check digit (ST)&gt; ^ &lt;code identifying the check digit scheme employed (ID)&gt; ^ &lt; assigning authority (HD)&gt; ^ &lt;identifier type code (IS)&gt; ^ &lt; assigning facility (HD)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The combination of values for <em>PersonIdentifier.ID, and PersonIdentifier.AssigningAuthority,</em> are intended to identify a person uniquely. The <em>PersonIdentifier.IDTypeCode</em> is useful for further filtering or to supply uniqueness in the event that the assigning authority may have more than one coding system.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Example: &#8230;&#8203;|112234<sup>^</sup>GOOD HEALTH HOSPITAL|&#8230;&#8203;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Only one PID.3 may be specified, only 1 segment pattern will be returned.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">PersonIdentifier.</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">ID</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">PID.3.1must be valued.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">PersonIdentifier</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Assigning Authority</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">PID.3.4 must be valued.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">PersonIdentifier</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Identifier type code</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">WhatDomainsReturned</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"></td>
